# ==================================
# Day 6 - Robustness & Edge Case Tests
# ==================================

### Test R1: Register with an empty username (should fail)
POST http://localhost:18080/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "",
    "password": "password123"
}


### Test R2: Register with a missing password key (should fail)
POST http://localhost:18080/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser"
}


### Test R3: Send a message to a non-existent recipient (should fail)
POST http://localhost:18080/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sender": "userA",
    "recipient": "ghost",
    "content": "Are you there?"
}


### Test R4: Send a message with a missing content key (should fail)
POST http://localhost:18080/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sender": "userA",
    "recipient": "userB"
}


### Test R5: Get messages for a user that doesn't exist (should fail)
GET http://localhost:18080/getMessages?username=ghost


### Test R6: Get messages without providing a username (should fail)
GET http://localhost:18080/getMessages